In this paper we empirically investigate the relation between diachronic change and synchronic variation in the word order of Dutch two-verb clusters.

[Download paper here](http://www.tntl.nl/index.php/tntl/article/view/424)

Recommended citation: Westendorp, Maud, Marieke Olthof, Jelke Bloem & Fred Weerman. 2018. Synchronic variation and diachronic change in Dutch two-verb clusters. <i>Tijdschrift voor Nederlandse Taal- en Letterkunde</i> 133(1): 34–60.
